{"id": "art-446", "label": "Art. 446", "title": "Art. 446: Intrarea în vigoare", "slug": "art-446", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 446: Intrarea în vigoare </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Prezentul cod intr&#259; în\nvigoare la data care va fi stabilit&#259; în legea pentru punerea în aplicare a\nacestuia, cu excep&#355;ia dispozi&#355;iilor alin. (2) &#351;i alin. (3), care\nintr&#259; în vigoare la 4 zile de la data public&#259;rii în Monitorul Oficial\nal României, Partea I, a prezentului cod.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>301/2004</span><span style='color:black'> - </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul penal</span><span style='color:black'>,\npublicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 575 din 29 iunie\n2004, cu modific&#259;rile ulterioare, &#351;i Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>294/2004</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nexecutarea pedepselor &#351;i a m&#259;surilor dispuse de organele judiciare în\ncursul procesului penal, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României,\nPartea I, nr. 591 din 1 iulie 2004, cu modific&#259;rile ulterioare, se\nabrog&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)În termen de 12 luni de la data\npublic&#259;rii prezentului cod în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I,\nGuvernul va supune Parlamentului spre adoptare proiectul de lege pentru punerea\nîn aplicare a Codului penal.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1503996637\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1027\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1503996637\"><![endif]></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n0in;margin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n0in;margin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>**</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1343945051\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1343945051\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Prezenta lege transpune dispozi&#355;iile art. 7 alin. (1),\nart. 12 alin. (3) &#351;i ale art. 14 alin. (3) din Directiva (UE) </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>2016/800</span><span style='color:black'> a Parlamentului\nEuropean &#351;i a Consiliului din 11 mai 2016 privind garan&#355;iile\nprocedurale pentru copiii care sunt persoane suspectate sau acuzate în cadrul\nprocedurilor penale, publicat&#259; în Jurnalul Oficial al Uniunii Europene,\nseria L, nr. 132 din 21 mai 2016.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>-****-</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Aceast&#259; lege a fost\nadoptat&#259; la data de 25 iunie 2009, în temeiul prevederilor art. 114 alin.\n(3) din Constitu&#355;ia României, republicat&#259;, în urma angaj&#259;rii\nr&#259;spunderii Guvernului în fa&#355;a Camerei Deputa&#355;ilor &#351;i a\nSenatului, în &#351;edin&#355;a comun&#259; din data de 22 iunie 2009.</span></p>\n\n\n<table class=MsoNormalTable border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0\n style='margin-left:5.75pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\n solid black 1.0pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>\n <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes;\n  height:2.25pt'>\n  <td width=705 valign=top style='width:529.0pt;border:solid black 1.0pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;height:2.25pt'>\n  \n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n  0in;margin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>PRE&#350;EDINTELE CAMEREI\n  DEPUTA&#354;ILOR</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n  0in;margin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span\n  style='color:black'>ROBERTA ALMA ANASTASE</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n  0in;margin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>PRE&#350;EDINTELE SENATULUI</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.25pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:\n  0in;margin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span\n  style='color:black'>MIRCEA-DAN GEOAN&#258;</span></b></p>\n\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>Publicat în Monitorul Oficial cu num&#259;rul\n510 din data de 24 iulie 2009</span></p>\n\n\n</div>\n<script>\n    // PARTEA 1: SCRIPTUL DE CĂUTARE (versiune corectată și finală cu normalizare)\n    const articlesIndex = [];\n    let currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = null;\n    let currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n    const activeArticleClassName = 'article-active-highlight-minimal';\n\n    const styleSheetSearch = document.createElement(\"style\");\n    styleSheetSearch.type = \"text/css\";\n    styleSheetSearch.innerText = `\n        .${activeArticleClassName} { \n            background-color: #e6f7ff !important; /* Un fundal albastru foarte deschis, subtil */\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        /* Stilurile pentru #customSearchContainer ar trebui să fie în HTML-ul interfeței de căutare, nu aici,\n           dar le las comentate dacă se dorește adăugarea lor dinamică, deși nu e recomandat pentru stiluri statice.\n        #customSearchContainer { \n            padding: 15px; \n            background-color: #f0f0f0; \n            border-bottom: 1px solid #dcdcdc; \n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        */\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a { \n            display: block; padding: 10px 12px; text-decoration: none; \n            color: #0056b3; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; \n            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a:hover { background-color: #f0f8ff; }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a.active-result-link { \n            background-color: #d4ebf7; font-weight: bold; color: #004085;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel a small { \n            color: #495057; display: block; margin-top: 4px; \n            font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.3;\n        }\n        #articleSearchResultsPanel .no-results {\n            padding: 15px; color: #6c757d; font-style: italic;\n        }\n    `;\n    document.head.appendChild(styleSheetSearch);\n\n    function normalizeText(text) {\n        if (typeof text !== 'string') return '';\n        text = text.toLowerCase();\n        text = text.replace(/ă/g, 'a').replace(/â/g, 'a').replace(/î/g, 'i').replace(/ș/g, 's').replace(/ş/g, 's').replace(/ț/g, 't').replace(/ţ/g, 't');\n        return text;\n    }\n\n    function isPotentiallyArticleTitle(text) {\n        return /^(Art\\.|Articolul)\\s*\\d+/i.test(text.trim().substring(0, 25));\n    }\n\n    function getArticleTitleAndNumber(text) {\n        const match = text.trim().match(/^(Art\\.|Articolul)\\s*(\\d+)\\s*[:\\-\\s]*(.*)/i);\n        if (match) {\n            const num = match[2];\n            let title = match[3] || \"\";\n            title = title.replace(/^\\s*\\(\\d+\\)/, '').trim();\n            const displayTitleFragment = title.length > 80 ? title.substring(0, 77) + \"...\" : title;\n            return { \n                number: num, \n                titleFragment: displayTitleFragment, \n                // CORECTAT AICI: Folosim template literals corect\n                fullDeclaration: `Art. ${num}${displayTitleFragment ? (': ' + displayTitleFragment) : ''}` \n            };\n        }\n        const fallbackTitle = text.length > 80 ? text.substring(0, 77) + \"...\" : text;\n        return { number: null, titleFragment: fallbackTitle, fullDeclaration: fallbackTitle };\n    }\n    \n    function isMajorHeading(text) {\n        const upperText = text.trim().toUpperCase();\n        if (upperText.length > 60) return false; \n        return upperText.startsWith(\"TITLUL\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"CAPITOLUL\") ||\n               upperText.startsWith(\"SECŢIUNEA\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"SECȚIUNEA\") || \n               upperText.startsWith(\"CARTEA\");\n    }\n\n    function buildArticlesIndex() {\n        articlesIndex.length = 0; \n        const paragraphs = document.body.getElementsByTagName('p');\n        let currentArticleData = null;\n        let articleGlobalIndex = 0;\n\n        for (let i = 0; i < paragraphs.length; i++) {\n            const pElement = paragraphs[i];\n            if (pElement.offsetParent === null && !(pElement.offsetWidth > 0 || pElement.offsetHeight > 0)) {\n                if (!pElement.textContent.trim() && pElement.innerHTML.toLowerCase().includes(\"&nbsp;\")) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n            }\n            const pTextOriginal = (pElement.textContent || pElement.innerText || \"\").trim();\n            if (!pTextOriginal) continue; \n\n            if (isPotentiallyArticleTitle(pTextOriginal)) {\n                if (currentArticleData) { articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); }\n                articleGlobalIndex++;\n                const uniqueId = `article-auto-${articleGlobalIndex}`;\n                pElement.id = uniqueId;\n                const titleInfo = getArticleTitleAndNumber(pTextOriginal);\n                currentArticleData = {\n                    id: uniqueId, titleElement: pElement,\n                    displayTitle: titleInfo.fullDeclaration, articleNumber: titleInfo.number,\n                    contentParagraphsElements: [pElement], fullTextContent: pTextOriginal,\n                    normalizedFullTextContent: normalizeText(pTextOriginal)\n                };\n            } else if (currentArticleData) { \n                if (isMajorHeading(pTextOriginal)) { \n                    articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); currentArticleData = null; \n                } else {\n                    currentArticleData.contentParagraphsElements.push(pElement);\n                    currentArticleData.fullTextContent += \"\\n\" + pTextOriginal;\n                    currentArticleData.normalizedFullTextContent += \"\\n\" + normalizeText(pTextOriginal);\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        if (currentArticleData) { articlesIndex.push(currentArticleData); }\n    }\n\n    function highlightTermInSnippet(snippet, termToHighlight) {\n        if (!snippet || !termToHighlight || termToHighlight.length === 0) return snippet;\n        const escapedTerm = termToHighlight.replace(/[.*+?^${}()|[\\]\\\\]/g, '\\\\$&');\n        try {\n            const regex = new RegExp(`(${escapedTerm})`, 'gi');\n            return snippet.replace(regex, '<mark>$1</mark>');\n        } catch (e) { \n            // console.error(\"Regex error in highlightTermInSnippet:\", e); // Opțional pentru debugging\n            return snippet; \n        }\n    }\n\n    function executeArticleSearch() {\n        if (articlesIndex.length === 0) { buildArticlesIndex(); }\n        const rawSearchTerm = document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').value.trim();\n        const normalizedSearchTerm = normalizeText(rawSearchTerm);\n        const resultsPanel = document.getElementById('articleSearchResultsPanel');\n        resultsPanel.innerHTML = ''; \n        removeCurrentHighlight();\n        if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) {\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link');\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n        }\n        if (!rawSearchTerm) {\n            resultsPanel.innerHTML = '\n<p class=\"no-results\">Introduceți un termen de căutare.</p>\n'; return;\n        }\n        const searchResults = [];\n        const isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch = rawSearchTerm.match(/^(art\\.|articolul)\\s*(\\d+)$/i);\n        const specificArticleNumberToSearch = isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch ? isSearchingForSpecificArticleNumberMatch[2] : null;\n\n        articlesIndex.forEach(article => {\n            let matchFound = false; \n            let snippetForDisplay = \"\"; // Aici vom stoca fragmentul relevant pentru afișare\n\n            if (specificArticleNumberToSearch) {\n                if (article.articleNumber === specificArticleNumberToSearch) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    // Pentru potrivire exactă de articol, afișăm începutul conținutului său\n                    snippetForDisplay = article.fullTextContent.substring(0, 150) + (article.fullTextContent.length > 150 ? \"...\" : \"\");\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm); \n                }\n            } else {\n                const normalizedArticleFullText = article.normalizedFullTextContent;\n                const normalizedDisplayTitle = normalizeText(article.displayTitle); \n                let termFoundInTitle = normalizedDisplayTitle.includes(normalizedSearchTerm);\n                let termFoundInContent = !termFoundInTitle && normalizedArticleFullText.includes(normalizedSearchTerm);\n\n                if (termFoundInTitle) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    // Dacă s-a găsit în titlu, snippet-ul poate fi o parte mai relevantă a conținutului\n                    const firstMatchIndexInNormalized = normalizedDisplayTitle.indexOf(normalizedSearchTerm); \n                    const searchWindowStart = Math.max(0, firstMatchIndexInNormalized - 30); \n                    const searchWindowEnd = Math.min(article.fullTextContent.length, firstMatchIndexInNormalized + normalizedSearchTerm.length + 70); \n                    snippetForDisplay = \"...\" + article.fullTextContent.substring(searchWindowStart, searchWindowEnd) + \"...\";\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm);\n\n                } else if (termFoundInContent) {\n                    matchFound = true;\n                    const firstMatchIndexInNormalized = normalizedArticleFullText.indexOf(normalizedSearchTerm);\n                    const searchWindowStart = Math.max(0, firstMatchIndexInNormalized - 30);\n                    const searchWindowEnd = Math.min(article.fullTextContent.length, firstMatchIndexInNormalized + normalizedSearchTerm.length + 70);\n                    snippetForDisplay = \"...\" + article.fullTextContent.substring(searchWindowStart, searchWindowEnd) + \"...\";\n                    snippetForDisplay = highlightTermInSnippet(snippetForDisplay, rawSearchTerm);\n                }\n            }\n            if (matchFound) { searchResults.push({ article: article, snippet: snippetForDisplay }); }\n        });\n\n        if (searchResults.length > 0) {\n            searchResults.forEach(result => {\n                const link = document.createElement('a');\n                link.href = `#${result.article.id}`; \n                // CORECTAT AICI: Folosim template literals corect și afișăm titlul + snippet-ul\n                link.innerHTML = `<strong>${result.article.displayTitle}</strong><br><small>${result.snippet}</small>`;\n                \n                link.onclick = function(e) {\n                    e.preventDefault();\n                    if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) { currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link'); }\n                    link.classList.add('active-result-link'); currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = link;\n                    scrollToArticleAndHighlight(result.article.id);\n                };\n                resultsPanel.appendChild(link);\n            });\n        } else { resultsPanel.innerHTML = '\n<p class=\"no-results\">Niciun articol găsit.</p>\n'; }\n    }\n    \n    function removeCurrentHighlight() {\n        if (currentlyHighlightedArticleElement) {\n            currentlyHighlightedArticleElement.classList.remove(activeArticleClassName);\n            currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = null;\n        }\n    }\n\n    function scrollToArticleAndHighlight(elementId) {\n        removeCurrentHighlight(); \n        const targetElement = document.getElementById(elementId);\n        if (targetElement) {\n             targetElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });\n            setTimeout(() => {\n                targetElement.classList.add(activeArticleClassName);\n                currentlyHighlightedArticleElement = targetElement;\n            }, 300); \n        }\n    }\n\n    function clearArticleSearch() {\n        document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').value = '';\n        document.getElementById('articleSearchResultsPanel').innerHTML = '';\n        removeCurrentHighlight();\n        if (currentlyActiveSearchResultLink) {\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink.classList.remove('active-result-link');\n            currentlyActiveSearchResultLink = null;\n        }\n    }\n\n    document.getElementById('articleSearchInput').addEventListener('keypress', function(event) {\n        if (event.key === 'Enter') { executeArticleSearch(); }\n    });\n\n    window.addEventListener('load', function() { /* buildArticlesIndex(); // Opțional */ });\n</script>\n\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"Legislation\",\n  \"name\": \"Codul Penal (Text Integral cu Căutare)\", // Adaptați\n  \"description\": \"Textul integral și actualizat al Codul Penal, cu funcție de căutare avansată pentru articole.\", // Adaptați\n  \"url\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro/legislatie/Codul Penal.html\", // Adaptați\n  \"inLanguage\": \"ro\",\n  \"provider\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"LegeaAplicata.ro\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro\"\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", // Adaptați: Data publicării acestei pagini web\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n     \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n     \"@id\": \"https://www.legeaaplicata.ro/legislatie/Codul Penal.html\" // Adaptați\n  }\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n\n</html>\n"}